IdxColumn NameDefinitionDescription

  contactInformation_postalCode varchar String representing the organization's postal code (zip code) as entered in their contact information.

  functions_array varchar Array representing the HRN and name of each function assigned to the organization.

Table ActionLog

{cube_name} table

IdxColumn NameDefinitionDescription
  dateActivated varchar Date/time field representing when a project first transitioned into the Active state.
  dateCompletedWorkflow varchar Date/time field representing when a project first entered a final state, i.e. completed the workflow.
  dateEnteredCurrentState varchar Date/time field representing when a project entered its current state.
  dateEnteredWorkflow varchar Date/time field representing when a project was last submitted into workflow, i.e. the last execution of the Submit action.
  dateEnteredCentralReview varchar Date/time field equivalent to the first time the proposal entered the \"Central Review\" state. This may be the same as Date Entered Workflow if unit review is NOT utilized for the proposal.
  dateProxyManaged varchar Date/time field representing when the proxy was last managed for a project, i.e. the last execution of the Manage Proxy action.
  transitionsToCentralOffice varchar Integer representing the number of times the project entered a state owned by the central office.
  transitionsToCounterparty varchar Integer representing the number of times the project entered a state owned by the counterparty.
  transitionsToPiStudyTeam varchar Integer representing the number of times the project entered a state owned by the PI/Study Team including pre-submission. This measure should represent the number of times PI/Study Team input was required after the submission entered the workflow.
  transitionsToDiscloser varchar Integer representing the number of times the project entered a state owned by the Discloser.
  transitionsToSponsor varchar Integer representing the number of times the project entered a state owned by the Sponsor.
  daysWithCentralOffice_calendar varchar Number representing calendar days the project was in a workflow state owned by the central office.
  daysWithCentralOffice_weekdays varchar Number representing weekdays the project was in a workflow state owned by the central office. This measure excludes Saturdays and Sundays. It includes holidays.
  daysWithPiStudyTeam_calendar varchar Number representing calendar days the project was in a workflow state owned by the PI/Study Team.
  daysWithPiStudyTeam_weekdays varchar Number representing weekdays the project was in a workflow state owned by the PI/Study Team. This measure excludes Saturdays and Sundays. It includes holidays.
  daysWithCounterparty_calendar varchar Number representing calendar days the project was in a workflow state owned by the counterparty.
  daysWithCounterparty_weekdays varchar Number representing weekdays the project was in a workflow state owned by the counterparty. This measure excludes Saturdays and Sundays. It includes holidays.
  daysWithDiscloser_calendar varchar Number representing calendar days the project was in a workflow state owned by the discloser.
  daysWithDiscloser_weekdays varchar Number representing weekdays the project was in a workflow state owned by the discloser. This measure excludes Saturdays and Sundays. It includes holidays.
  daysWithSponsor_calendar varchar Number representing calendar days the project was in a workflow state owned by the sponsor.
  daysWithSponsor_weekdays varchar Number representing weekdays the project was in a workflow state owned by the sponsor. This measure excludes Saturdays and Sundays. It includes holidays.
  daysInProgress_weekdays varchar Number representing total weekdays the project was in the workflow from the date it FIRST entered workflow. This excludes days in PreSubmission or in a final state, and excludes Saturdays and Sundays. It includes holidays.
  daysInProgress_calendar varchar Number representing total calendar days the project was in the workflow from the date it FIRST entered workflow. This excludes days in PreSubmission or in a final state.
  id_pk varchar String representing the generated hash key on a combination of fields that create uniqueness for a record. This represents the primary key for the table.
  hrn varchar String representing the HRN of the action record. This ID is not displayed in the UI and is used for joins in the database.
  correlationId varchar String representing the ID used for change tracking.
  actionDate time Date/time field representing the date the action was logged.
  actionType varchar String representing the action type ID.
  sourceStateId varchar String representing the ID of the workflow state the project was in before the action was logged.
  targetStateId varchar String representing the ID of the workflow state the project entered after the action was logged. If the record is created to track days the project is in its current state, targetStateId is 'CurrentState'.
  timeInMilliseconds varchar Integer representing the interval of time that passed since the last action logged to the project. Populated whenever there is a state change associated with the action.
  daysInSourceState_calendar varchar Calendar days between the start and end dates that the project was in the source workflow state.
  daysInSourceState_weekdays varchar Weekdays between the start and end dates that the project was in the source workflow state. This excludes weekends (Saturday and Sunday) but does not exclude holidays.
project_hrn varchar String representing the HRN of the project to which the action was logged. This ID is not displayed in the UI but is used for joins in the database.
  dateModified time Date/time field representing the time when the action was last updated with notification details.
  showInHistory varchar Boolean true/false indicating whether the action appears in the action log widget for the project.
  documents_array varchar String representing the array of document information related to the action.
tenant_id varchar The id value for the tenant associated to the action record.
  isRestricted varchar Boolean true/false indicating whether the action is a special case with permission restrictions.
  author_person_hrn varchar String representing the HRN of the person who authored the action. This ID is not displayed in the UI but is used for joins in the database.
  sourceStateOwningGroup varchar The group responsible for the project in the action source state, i.e. the state the project was in before the action occurred. Where a record is created to track days the project is in its current state, this represents the owning group of the project in its current state.
  targetStateOwningGroup varchar The group responsible for the project in the action target state, i.e. the state the project entered after the action occurred. When a record is ceated to track days the project has been in its current state, targetStateOwningGroup is NULL.
  sourceStateSummaryState varchar A grouping applied to the the source project state, i.e. the state the project was in before the action occurred, to facilitate metrics reporting. Where a record is created to track days the project is in its current state, this represents the summary state of the project in its current state.
